title: ROB BOYCE - BEST SKATE TRICK AT THE AUSTRALIAN OPEN OF SURFI
description:
Hurley -- Australian Open of Surfing -- Manly 2012 -- Day 9
Back it up - Yeah Rob! He may be 42 years of age and one of the oldest competitors at the Australian Open of Surfing Beach Bowl but that didn't stop Rob "Sluggo" Boyce pulling off the Best Trick win with an epic backflip. Persistence does pay off.
